{"prompt": "Generate a website for a personalized tutoring service. The website should be vibrant and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Personalized Tutoring Services</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e53935; /* Vibrant Red */\n            --secondary-color: #ffcdd2; /* Light Pinkish Red */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --hover-color: #c62828;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color), #f44336);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);\n            background-size: 20px 20px;\n            opacity: 0.5;\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-section {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            text-align: center;\n            flex: 1 1 300px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        .cta-section {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n            padding: 50px 20px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color), #f44336);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-section h2 {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid transparent;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            border-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            .service-section {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: center;\n            }\n            .service-item {\n                width: 80%;\n            }\n            .cta-section h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .cta-button {\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Ignite Your Learning Potential</h1>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);\">Personalized Tutoring for Academic Success</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Personalized Approach</h2>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 20px auto;\">We believe every student learns differently. Our expert tutors tailor their methods to your unique needs, ensuring you grasp concepts thoroughly and build confidence.</p>\n\n        <div class=\"service-section\">\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>One-on-One Attention</h3>\n                <p>Dedicated sessions focused solely on your learning goals and challenges.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Customized Learning Plans</h3>\n                <p>Strategies and materials designed specifically to address your strengths and weaknesses.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Expert & Passionate Tutors</h3>\n                <p>Our tutors are highly qualified, experienced, and committed to your success.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"cta-section\">\n        <h2>Ready to Transform Your Grades?</h2>\n        <p>Let's unlock your academic potential together.</p>\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Book Your Free Consultation</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Have questions or want to schedule your first session? Fill out the form below!</p>\n        <form style=\"max-width: 600px; margin: 30px auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 15px;\">\n            <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 4px;\">\n            <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 4px;\">\n            <textarea placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required style=\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 4px;\"></textarea>\n            <button type=\"submit\" style=\"background-color: var(--brand-color); color: white; padding: 15px 30px; border: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 1.1em; cursor: pointer; transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\">Send Message</button>\n        </form>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Personalized Tutoring Services. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add some subtle animation or interactivity if desired.\n        // For this concise example, we'll keep it minimal.\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}